title: Bastyr University Cafeteria
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Organic, Buffet, Salad bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Previously all veg. Cafeteria of naturpathic University with some vegan options. Food is served cafeteria-style and mostly priced per pound. Offers a few hot dishes that rotate daily and large salad bar, desserts. Ingredients of each item are listed.
